Le app yovavanyo yekhamera yewebhu ekwi-intanethi ikhululekile ngokupheleleyo ukuyisebenzisa ngaphandle kobhaliso.
Akukho kufakelo olufunekayo ukuze uvavanye kwaye ulungise ikhamera yakho yewebhu ngaphandle kwesidingo sokukhathazeka malunga nokhuseleko lwekhompyuter.
Ubumfihlo bakho bukhuselwe ngokupheleleyo, uvavanyo lwekhamera yewebhu luqhutywa ngokupheleleyo ngaphakathi kwisikhangeli sakho kwaye akukho datha yevidiyo ithunyelwa kwi-intanethi.
Ukuba kwi-intanethi, le app yokuvavanya ikhamera yewebhu ixhaswa zizo zonke izixhobo ezinomkhangeli zincwadi.
Ngaba ujonge ukuvavanya imakrofoni yakho endaweni yoko? Zama i-olu vavanyo lwe-mic ukuvavanya zombini kwaye ufumane izisombululo zokulungisa imakrofoni yakho.
Ngaba uyafuna ukurekhoda ividiyo kwikhamera yakho? Zama i-oku kulula ukuyisebenzisa kunye nokurekhoda ividiyo kwi-intanethi ukurekhoda ividiyo kwikhamera yakho kanye kwisikhangeli sakho.
Iinkcazelo zeempawu zekhamera
Umgangatho wento
Umlinganiselo wembonakalo yesisombululo sekhamera: o.t. ububanzi besisombululo bohlulwe ngobude besisombululo
Umgangatho wefreyimu
Ireyithi yesakhelo linani lezakhelo (i-static snapshots) ikhamera ibamba ngesekondi nganye.
Ubude
Ubude besisombululo sekhamera.
Ububanzi
Ububanzi besisombululo sekhamera.

Ngaphambi kokukhuphela okanye ukukhuphela i-MediaWiki, unokuthatha isigqibo sokuba uza kuyicinezela itafile ngokweemfuno zakho.
Qaphela: Idata yakho ukholosile, le amaguquka yenziwa ngokupheleleyo kwibhrawuza yakho web kwaye asiyi ukugcina nayiphi na idata yakho.
I-HTML imele i-hypertext yophawu lophawu. I-HTML yikhowudi esetyenziselwa ukwakha iphepha lewebhu kunye nomxholo, iziqendu, uluhlu, imifanekiso kunye neetafile, njl njl.

- INkomfa yeHlabathi yezoKhenketho lwe-Eco ibanjwa phantse kwi-intanethi phantsi kombutho weTaiwan Ecotourism Association.
- USrilal uza kube esenza intetho ephambili kusuku lokuqala lwesi siganeko sibalulekileyo seentsuku ezimbini.
- Umxholo weseshoni yokuqala uthi "Iimpendulo kuPhuhliso loKhenketho lwe-Ecotourism phantsi kwe-COVID-19."
Inkomfa, eya kubanjwa phantse/kwi-intanethi, iququzelelwa yi I-Taiwan Ecotourism Association (TEA). Kuya kubakho iiseshini ezintathu ezisasazwa kwezi ntsuku zimbini, kwaye izithethi ezininzi ezibalaseleyo ziya kube zinikela intetho.
Kwiseshoni yoku-1 phantsi komxholo othi “Impendulo Ekuphuhliseni Indlela yoKhenketho lwe-Ecotourism phantsi kwe-COVID-19,” uSrilal uza kube ehambisa intetho ephambili enesihloko esithi “Ukukhusela iBiodiversity-Post COVID Tourism?”
USrilal wayeyi-CEO ye-Serendib Leisure iminyaka engaphezu kwe-10, kwaye emva koko wakhokela iprojekthi yeCeylon Chamber / EU, TSHINTSHA i-ASIA Greening iihotele zaseSri Lanka ngempumelelo iminyaka emine. Ngoku udla umhlala-phantsi kwaye ubandakanyeka kumsebenzi wokucebisana ne-ADB, i-GiZ, kunye ne-MDF (inyathelo le-Australia lamazwe amaninzi). Usebenza kwiibhodi zeLaugfs Leisure kunye ne-Asian Eco Tourism Network.

Kwaye oku, ngaphezulu okanye ngapha

anon uzama ukuthatha iTriforce ukoyisa umhlaba, kwaye uZelda kunye neLink bazama ukuyiphepha. Mhlawumbi yiloo nto Ngokuphinda iskimu esele sisenzile ngaphakathi, isaga yevidiyo iyakwazi ukusibambisa kakhulu (kwaye ngesihendo silingane neekomikhi, iithoyi, iikonsathi ...).

Nge-NS6 uza kuba nakho ukulawula abathengi bakho, unxibelelane nabo kwaye ube nakho ukubabela kwiindawo zakho zentengiso ngokukhawuleza nangokufanelekileyo. Isixhobo esijolise kuphela kule marike.
Bhalisa indawo ezintsha zentengiso, hlaziya ulwazi lwakho okanye uzicime. Kwi-NS6 le nkqubo iyakhawuleza kwaye iyasebenza; layisha iifoto okanye ubophe iindawo zakho zentengiso kubaxhasi bakho.
Gcina ulwazi lwakho luhlelekile kwaye lukhuselekile efini; ivumela lonke iqela lakho ukuba lifikelele kulwazi oluhlaziyiweyo ngexesha lokwenyani, elilungele iinkampani ezineendawo zentengiso kwimimandla eyahlukeneyo.
Iindawo zakho zentengiso ziya kuvela kuyo yonke inethiwekhi yabathengi be-NS6 yeMedia, ekuvumela ukuba ufikelele kubathengi bakweminye imimandla kwaye uvale isivumelwano ngokulula. Uqhakamshelwano kwi-NS6 luthe ngqo kuwe, ngaphandle kwabalamli.

Nangona kunjalo, uye wasishiya sisebenza kwiindawo ezahlukeneyo España. Ngokuqhelekileyo, ezi yayiziikhomishini ezivela kwiintsapho ze-aristocratic zexesha labo, ezifana, ngokomzekelo, ukuba UMarquis waseCo
... (4021 chars skipped) ... 
na. Ngaphaya koko, ikwangowe- isigaba se-neo-gothic yomakhi. UGaudí wafunda isiCatalan kunye neCastilian Gothic nzulu ukuze ayifunxe aze ayichaze ngokutsha ngemigangatho yakhe yokwakha.
Kwimeko nayiphi na into, ibhotwe le-episcopal liphinde likhawulwe ngaphandle njenge Nqaba ephakathi. Ineplani yomnqamlezo yamaGrike kunye neenqaba ezine zecylindrical kwiikona, kunye nomjelo ojikelezayo. ... (4021 chars skipped) ...
lela, i-basalt kunye namatye e-limestone, izitena ze-ceramic, iglasi, udaka kunye ne-Foundry slag. Kwaye konke oku kwenza yonke into ehambelanayo apho kungekho nqongophala yeenkcukacha zokuhlobisa ezifana, umzekelo, iibhentshi ezinamadolo.
Ukuqukumbela, sikubonise eyona iphambili UGaudí usebenza ngaphandle kweBarcelona. Kodwa kukho omnye onjengaye Indawo yokuhlala yaseCatllaras kunye Ngaba iigadi zeArtigas, zombini eLa Pobla de Lillet. Yiza ufumane yonke le misebenzi yomyili omkhulu waseCatalan.

Umdlalo wokulinganisa, ofana nomdlalo wevenkile okanye wokupheka, yindlela eyonwabisayo yokucinga ukuba kunjani ukuba ngabanye abantu abathatha inxaxheba kwimisebenzi eyahlukileyo. Umdlalo wokulinganisa uyabancedisa abantwana ukuba baqonde ilizwe abahleli kulo kunye nezinto abazibona zisenzeka. Uphinda ubancedise ekubeni babe nomfanekiso ngqondweni wamava ahlukileyo abanokuncokola okanye babhale ngawo.
Cofa apha ngezantsi ukumamela isicatshulwa
Abantwana abaselula bayakonwabela kakhulu ukubalisa amabali besebenzisa umdlalo wokulinganisa. Ukudlala ngolu hlobo ke kuyabanceda bacinge futhi baqonde ilizwe abahleli kulo.
Ukubalisa amabali kuphinda kubancede bakwazi ukuphuhlisa imifanekiso-ntelekelelo yabo. Ukudlala ngolu hlobo kukhuthaza abantwana ukuba bazenzele umfanekiso ntelekelelo wamabali abanokuwabalisela abanye abantu ze ekugqibeleni bawabhale.
Umdlalo wokulinganisa wonwabisa ngakumbi ke xa umntwana wakho eneepropu ezihambelana nebali abalilinganisayo. Ukuba umntwana wakho wenza ngathi wenza isuphu, kufuneka asebenzise into enkulu emile okwesangqa, efana nembiza yokupheka isuphu ze asebenzise uluthi enze ngalo icephe lesuphu.
Izinto ezincinci ezifana namagqabi okanye imifanekiso yemifuno zingagalelwa embizeni zizanyiswe ngeli xesha besenza ngathi bayapheka ngokwendlela abenza ngayo abantu abadala emakhaya.

Obengumanejala kumasipala iEnoch Mgijima uNokuthula Cecilia Zondani (52) uzakube evela kwiiNkundla zamaTyala eMonti ngomhla we11 kuSeptemba malunga nezityholo abekwe zona ezokuthoba ngomlenze imali ezizigidi zeerandi.
UZondani uvelile kule veki ezinkundleni kuKomani emva kokuba ethe wabanjwa ziiHawks eMpuma Koloni, nalapho akhululwe ngebheyile yeR5000.
Kutyholwa ukuba, ngethuba uZondani engumanejala kamasipala waseEnoch Mgijima nophantsi kweANC, ibhunga lenza isivumelwano sengqesho seenyanga eziyi-36 nomboneleli-nkonzo malunga nokubonelela ngoomatshini obolekisayo wokulima.
Ngokwengxelo ephuma kwisithethi seeHawks eMpuma Koloni uYolisa Mgolodela, ithi, ibhunga laphumeza isivumelwano, sentlawulo ye-R1.2 yezigidi zeerandi ngenyanga kumboneleli-nkonzo, kutyholwa ukuba uZondani uye wasitshintsha ngokungekho mthethweni isivumelwano – ngaphandle kwemvume yebhunga naba phezulu kulo masipala– wagunyazisa ukuhlawulwa kwe-R2.4 yezigidi zeerandi ngenyanga.
UMgolodela uthi ityala liqhubeka eMonti kwinyanga ezayo lisusiwe kuKomani.
Impondo Elisha lonwabisa ngomculo walo eGqobhasi kuloMgqibelo

NgoMeyi 10, uMboniso wokuqala weeMveliso zoMthengi waseTshayina wafikelela esiphelweni eHainan International Convention and Exhibition Centre. Itotali yamashishini angama-1,505 kunye neemveliso ze-2,628 zabathengi abavela kumazwe angama-70 kunye nemimandla ethathe inxaxheba kwi-4-day Expo, efumana ngaphezu kwe-30,000 yabathengi ababhalisiweyo begama lokwenene kunye neendwendwe ezichwephesha, kwaye ngaphezu kwe-240,000 iindwendwe zangena kwi-Expo. Njengokuphela kwenkampani yezikhephe, i-Weihai Ruiyang yonyulwa kwigqiza laseShandong lomboniso.
Kulo mboniso, u-Weihai Ruiyang weza neemveliso ezimbini ezidumileyo, uKhenketho lwebhodi yokubheqa ene-inflatable kunye ne-RY-BD yesikhephe esineflatable. Zombini ezi mveliso zatsala abathengi abavela kwihlabathi liphela ukuba bandwendwele nje ukuba bavele. ISikhululo sikamabonakude saseShandong, isitishi seTV saseHainan, iQilu Evening News kunye namanye amajelo eendaba beza kudliwano-ndlebe, bafikelela kwinjongo yentsebenziswano yokuqala kunye nabarhwebi basePoland nabaseFransi kwangoko, kwaye babenonxibelelwano olunzulu nabathengi basekhaya kunye nababoneleli bezinto eziphathekayo.
Ixesha lokuposa: Jun-22-2021

Ngaba uyafuna ukusebenzisa iPC yakho ngokungathi yiMac? Kule posi sichaza indlela yokusebenzisa umatshini we-macOS obonakalayo kwiWindows.
Ukuba uyazibuza ukuba yintoni i-MsMpEng.exe, apha sinempendulo kunye nendlela yokuyiyeka ekusebenziseni izixhobo zekhompyuter yakho.
Fumanisa apha inyathelo ngenyathelo ukuba ungazicima njani iifayile kwiWindows kwikhompyuter ye-CMD usebenzisa i-DEL command kunye neempawu zayo eziyimfuneko.
Fumanisa apha ukuba ungawuthatha njani umfanekiso wekhusi ngewindows inyathelo ngenyathelo nakwenye ikhompyuter enenkqubo yokusebenza yeWindows.
Fumana apha ukuba zeziphi iinguqulelo ze Windows 10, 8 kunye no-7 ongenako ukwenza ukuba uqhagamshelo lwidesktop ekude (i-RDP).

MPUMA KOLONI- Bezithe bhazalala kwiimvaba ngeemvaba iinkokheli ezikwangabathunywa bombutho ophetheyo i-African National Congress(ANC), ephondweni.
Ezinkokheli uninzi lwazo bezikhuthaza abantu ukuba babhalisele uvoto nanjengoko kungasentsuku zatywala lugaleleke usuku lokuvota.
Kodwa eyona nto ingamandla, bebeyocela imithandazo ukuze ulonyulo lusulungeke, luzimele kwaye lungabinamkhethe.
Inkulumbuso yephondo leMpuma Koloni Lubabalo Oscar Mabuyane ubeyizimase eKWT Methodist Church eQonce.
Ilungu lePEC elikwanguMphathiswa weSebe lezeMfundo uFundile Gade uye watyelela ibandla laseGod’s Heart Family Church.
Elinye ilungu lePEC uBukiwe Fanta ubeyizimase le nkonzo eCwecweni Methodist Church.
Ongowokuqala ngqa usekela-nobhala jikelele uNomvula Mokonyane uye waziminca ngeMethodist Church of Southern Africa, Kumkani Hintsa, Dutywa Circuit 330.
UMphathiswa weSebe lezemidlalo, Ubugcisa nenkcubeko, aphinde abelilungu lePEC, uNonceba Kontsiwe ubeduda nabazalwane baseSonwabile Community Hall eNqanqarhu Village kwawadi 3.
Elinye ilungu lePEC elikwanguMphathiswa weSebe lezothutho kunye nokhuseleko uXolile Nqatha ubebheshuza eFree Salvation Church, eGqeberha.
Ukanti yena usekela-nobhala kundlunkulu wepalamente yaseBisho uHelen Sauls-August, ubezimase le nkonzo eSt Patrick’s Church eBuffalo City, ngelixesha uSiyabulela Zangqa olilungu lePEC ubetyityimba eAfrican Gospel Church kuwadi 8 eWalter Sisulu.

Esebenzayo
Sijonge ukusebenza okugqwesileyo kuzo zonke iimveliso kunye neenkonzo zethu. Ekugqibeleni, oko kuthetha umgangatho obalaseleyo womngxuma kunye nokwembiwa ngexabiso eliphantsi kuwe.
Egqwesileyo
Singomnye wabenzi besixhobo sokomba amatye eTshayina. Iimveliso zethu zanamhlanje ziya kukunika i-edge ehamba phambili.
Comprehensive
Sikunika izixhobo ze-tophammer kunye nezixhobo ze-DTH kwisicelo ngasinye, njengokumbiwa kwemigodi ephantsi komhlaba kunye ne-tunneling, imigodi yomhlaba, ukugrunjwa kwamaqula kunye neekwari, kunye neendlela kunye nokwakhiwa.
